text: Dedovsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Yermolayevsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Dedovsky
